üìó MCQ SET ‚Äì 7 (Trick Questions)
31. Snow devices can act as temporary storage when internet is unavailable.

True / False?

‚úÖ Answer: True

32. Snowmobile can process data like EC2 instances.

True / False?

‚úÖ Answer: False
Snowmobile = storage only, not compute.

33. OpsHub must be used from the AWS Console.

A. True
B. False

‚úÖ Answer: B
OpsHub is local desktop GUI, not a console-only tool.

34. Removing the TPM chip exposes customer data.

A. True
B. False

‚úÖ Answer: B
Data is encrypted with AES-256; TPM only enforces tamper detection.

35. Snowcone is heavier and higher capacity than Snowball.

A. True
B. False

‚úÖ Answer: B
Snowcone < Snowball in size & capacity.
